<i>adjective</i>: 청렴하다 [청념하다], 청렴결백하다 [청념결배카다], 강직하다 [강지카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>청렴하다 [청념하다]</dt><br>
<dd>incorruptible; dignified</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 깨끗하고 욕심이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being morally sound and free from greed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>청렴결백하다 [청념결배카다]</dt><br>
<dd>incorruptible; dignified</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 맑고 깨끗하며 욕심이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having a pure, clear mind and being free from greed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>강직하다 [강지카다]</dt><br>
<dd>upright; incorruptible</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 꼿꼿하고 바르다.</dd><br>
<dd>The personality trait of being straightforward, honest and impervious to corruption.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>